      <PointerOffset>37320</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_002_039_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;MEL&gt;、おなか空いてない？
なにか食べなくて平気？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;MEL&gt;, aren’t you hungry? Are you sure you don’t need to eat something?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <StructId>1</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>24</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37720</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_002_039_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うん、平気だよ、全然</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah, I’m fine. Totally fine.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <StructId>2</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38224</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_002_039_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;MEL&gt;、その『全然』、違うぞ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;MEL&gt;, you’re using “totally” wrong.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <StructId>3</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38924</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_002_039_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え？　どういうこと？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? What do you mean?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <StructId>4</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39232</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_002_039_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>『全然』の後には、必ず否定の言葉が来んだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>“Totally” is always followed by a negative word.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <StructId>5</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39832</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_002_039_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だから、全然ダメ、とか
全然おもしろくねーとかはいいけど</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So, “totally bad” or “totally not funny” is fine...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <StructId>6</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40516</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_002_039_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>全然いいとか、全然面白いとかは
違うんだぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But “totally good” or “totally funny” is wrong.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <StructId>7</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41260</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_002_039_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>へぇ……さすが、色々と
本読んでるだけあるね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wow... You really do read a lot of books.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <StructId>8</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41512</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_002_039_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クリュル〜</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kryll~</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <StructId>9</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>14</UnknownPointer>
